text: Potamophylax is a genus of insects belonging to the family Limnephilidae. ==Species== List of species includes: * Potamophylax albergaria Malicky, 1976 * Potamophylax alpinus Tobias, 1994 * Potamophylax coronavirus * Potamophylax juliani Kumanski, 1999 * Potamophylax winneguthi * Potamophylax qafshtamaensis ==References== Category:Insects
title: Potamophylax (insect)
